<li id="cite_note-28"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.netkurd.org/nuce_bixwine.asp?id=11642" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.netkurd.org/nuce_bixwine.asp?id=11642" rel="nofollow">[2]</a> Among the Yazidis, this festival is celebrated on the first Wednesday of Nisan (April) which marks the first day of their new year (rather than March 21st). It is also called <i>Cejna Sersal</i>(New Year's Feast)<a href="http://www.berbang.org/berbang/carsema_sor.htm" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.berbang.org/berbang/carsema_sor.htm" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.yek-dem.com/IMAGES/R9-79.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.yek-dem.com/IMAGES/R9-79.pdf" rel="nofollow">[4]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-Encyclop.C3.A6dia_Iranica_DIVINATION-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Encyclop.C3.A6dia_Iranica_DIVINATION_30-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFOMIDSALAR">OMIDSALAR, MAHMOUD. <a href="http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v7f4/v7f482.html" class="external text" title="http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v7f4/v7f482.html" rel="nofollow">"DIVINATION"</a>. <i>Encyclopedia Iranica</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v7f4/v7f482.html" class="external free" title="http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v7f4/v7f482.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.iranica.com/newsite/index.isc?Article=http://www.iranica.com/newsite/articles/unicode/v7f4/v7f482.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-04-05</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=DIVINATION&amp;rft.atitle=Encyclopedia+Iranica&amp;rft.aulast=OMIDSALAR&amp;rft.aufirst=MAHMOUD&amp;rft.au=OMIDSALAR%2C+MAHMOUD&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iranica.com%2Fnewsite%2Findex.isc%3FArticle%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.iranica.com%2Fnewsite%2Farticles%2Funicode%2Fv7f4%2Fv7f482.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Nowruz"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
